    <item>
      <title>加纳寻求限制部分供应，可可期货上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/cocoa-futures-advance-as-ghana-seeks-to-restrict-some-supplies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳计划限制下一季的部分供应，这引发了人们对持续短缺的担忧，导致可可期货上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/cocoa-futures-advance-as-ghana-seeks-to-restrict-some-supplies</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 11:04:12 GMT</pubDate>
